channel.title: My Eulogy
channel.description:
First of all id like to say thanks to the many people that made me laugh the past year or so, you guys may all hate me,(thats sorta why im leaving) but you gave me a hell of a lot to do over the past year.
I'd also like to personally thank CatzEyes93 (as well as all of the other mods) for nat banning me as long as they did, it was a fun run, and i look forward to the day that BMS is complete.
I will come back here ever so often just to see what you guys are up to (that is if you guys dont ban me, which i hope you wont :slight_smile: ) and i may post something from time to time, but not as often as i used to, like maybe something once every month, give or take. I may not even come back here at all.
So now you may be asking yourself "why is swampfox making a crappy thread about his departure?" well as you all very well may know, i am a well behaved mentally retarded child :smiley: and because of that i dont know better.
You may also be wondering why im leaving. Well there are many reasons why im leaving, but the main one is because everyone hates me here, so i think i have overstayed my welcome. Another reason is because there are so many retards on that i dont know how anyone could bare to stay another minuet in this hellish place, but dont get me wrong, i love to troll this this place, it really pisses a lot of people off, i love this place too. But my suggestion is that you should maybe put an age limit on here or something, because.......i mean.....damn, so many (as i have learned my being here) kids under the age of 15 (including myself) are fucking douches.
So in the end if you want to congratulate the people who finally made me leave, you can thank Mr.shadow, Bolteh, OldDirtyBastard, CTID, and rot)(fodder
please dont say thank god that im gone (even though you probably will) but just remeber all the fun times we had together
thank you and goodbye
P.S as a goodbye i will leave a picture of myself in the post a picture of yourself thread
